The '''Rulaarian pleasure yacht''' was a civilian [[Starship/Legends|starship]] that existed during the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]]. One such [[Rulaar]]ian [[Yacht/Legends|yacht]] was destroyed by the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]] as it departed [[The Wheel/Legends|the Wheel]], a [[Casino/Legends|casino]]-ridden [[Space station/Legends|space station]] popular amongst [[Gambling/Legends|gamblers]].<ref name="Deathgame">[[Star Wars (1977) 20|''Star Wars'' (1977) 20]]</ref>

